high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white dresser.
Pick up the silver disc to the left of the book on the dresser.
Turn left and walk to the side of the dresser on the right with the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a silver disc by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the drawer cabinet to your right and look down.
Grab the CD on the drawer cabinet.
Look up, turn left, walk straight, quickly turn right, walk to the mirror on the wall, when you reach the mirror on the wall, turn right to face the lamp and look down.
Turn on the lamp on the drawer cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Grab a CD on the drawer cabinet and turn on the lamp on the drawer cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and take a small step to your left and walk to the dresser in front of you.
Pick up the cd that's in front of you on the dresser.
Take a step to your left then walk to the wall then turn right to face the lamp.
Turn on the lamp that's on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a cd by lamp light.
